children.name: Rules
children.text: This tiny mechanical insectoid can be attached to a suit of medium or heavy armor. Once it is attached, it cannot be removed without losing its magical properties. The beetle scuttles about throughout the day mending and cleaning the armor. Each day at dawn the armor is considered fully repaired for any damage it has suffered. Armor maintained with such care improves in quality, allowing the wearer to use a reaction once per day to increase their AC by 4 when they are targeted with a melee or ranged weapon attack.
